  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Help JACK BARAU, the pirate petrel, save his species!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wander across the island in search of lost fledglings. Each night, artificial lights disorient the <strong>Barau’s petrels</strong>, leaving the young birds at the mercy of lurking rats and stray cats. Gather a fragile but hopeful parade, and lead them to the ocean—where they can finally take flight toward freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras/12424863f1c2979b3e772716e07148ae.poster.avif?t=1751183255\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras/12424863f1c2979b3e772716e07148ae.webm?t=1751183255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras/12424863f1c2979b3e772716e07148ae.mp4?t=1751183255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JACK BARAU</strong> is a poetic, quirky and heartfelt 2D puzzle-platformer. Inspired by a poignant ecological reality, it puts you in the feathers of an old pirate with a tender heart, the last hope for a critically endangered species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide Jack with precision through diverse environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and protect the fledglings in a growing line of life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid deadly predators and nighttime hazards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trigger traps and activate switches to overcome obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a stylized world full of humor, emotion, and environmental awareness.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Designed to resonate with players of all ages,</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JACK BARAU</strong> is a touching adventure — a loving tribute to the real-life Barau’s petrel, a rare seabird native to the highlands of Réunion Island, and to all those working to save it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras/ebacd49f339b4a2dc95f690e62d6c2dc.avif?t=1751183255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras_big/ebacd49f339b4a2dc95f690e62d6c2dc.avif?t=1751183255 width=800 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Help JACK BARAU, the pirate petrel, save his species!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wander across the island in search of lost fledglings. Each night, artificial lights disorient the <strong>Barau’s petrels</strong>, leaving the young birds at the mercy of lurking rats and stray cats. Gather a fragile but hopeful parade, and lead them to the ocean—where they can finally take flight toward freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras/12424863f1c2979b3e772716e07148ae.poster.avif?t=1751183255\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras/12424863f1c2979b3e772716e07148ae.webm?t=1751183255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras/12424863f1c2979b3e772716e07148ae.mp4?t=1751183255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JACK BARAU</strong> is a poetic, quirky and heartfelt 2D puzzle-platformer. Inspired by a poignant ecological reality, it puts you in the feathers of an old pirate with a tender heart, the last hope for a critically endangered species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide Jack with precision through diverse environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and protect the fledglings in a growing line of life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid deadly predators and nighttime hazards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trigger traps and activate switches to overcome obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a stylized world full of humor, emotion, and environmental awareness.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Designed to resonate with players of all ages,</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JACK BARAU</strong> is a touching adventure — a loving tribute to the real-life Barau’s petrel, a rare seabird native to the highlands of Réunion Island, and to all those working to save it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras/ebacd49f339b4a2dc95f690e62d6c2dc.avif?t=1751183255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606740/extras_big/ebacd49f339b4a2dc95f690e62d6c2dc.avif?t=1751183255 width=800 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
